OL,3,CConservative leader's 20mph tweet
OL,4,C'brought Senedd into disrepute'
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservative leader in the
OL,7,FSenedd brought the Welsh Parliament
OL,8,Finto disrepute by calling Wales' 20mph
OL,9,Fspeed limit a "blanket" policy on
OL,10,Fsocial media, according to a Senedd
OL,11,Fstandards committee.
OL,13,FAndrew RT Davies had said that his
OL,14,Fchoice of words was "a matter of
OL,15,Fopinion" but he is due to be
OL,16,Fofficially reprimanded next week in
OL,17,FCardiff Bay.
