OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has said the
OL,7,F"blanket" description of the policy is
OL,8,Fwrong because the default limit in
OL,9,Fbuilt-up areas, which was previously
OL,10,F30mph, is subject to exemptions.
OL,12,FThe Senedd's standards commissioner
OL,13,FDouglas Bain said that as: "Leader of
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Conservatives and a former
OL,15,Fexperienced member of the Standards of
OL,16,FConduct Committee it was incumbent of
OL,17,Fthe Member to set a good example and
OL,18,Fto follow the guidance given by the
OL,19,FCommittee and in the Guidance on the
OL,20,FCode of Conduct."
