OL,6,FThe committee report noted two
OL,7,Fseparate complaints in relation to Mr
OL,8,FDavies' tweet which used the phrase
OL,9,F"blanket" in relation to the
OL,10,Fapplication of the 20mph speed limit
OL,11,Fon social media.
OL,13,FIt said: "Another bus route cut thanks
OL,14,Fto Labour and Plaid's blanket 20mph
OL,15,Fspeed limits."
OL,17,FIt was posted after the finding of the
OL,18,FSenedd's Standards of Conduct
OL,19,FCommittee that the term "blanket" was
OL,20,F"imprecise and inaccurate".
