OL,6,FIn a response, Mr Davies said: The
OL,7,FStandards Committee recently
OL,8,Fconsidered usage of the term "blanket"
OL,9,Fto describe the new 20mph speed limit
OL,10,Fin Wales. The Committee agreed that,
OL,11,Fwhen using the term, I was expressing
OL,12,Fa value judgment and not a statement
OL,13,Fof fact. While the
OL,15,FCommittee believed that this
OL,16,Fdescription was incorrect, this was a
OL,17,Fmatter of opinion. As such, enhanced
OL,18,Fprotection under Article 10 of the
OL,19,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights
OL,20,Fmeant that it had to be tolerated."
