OL,6,FThe committee said it "considers a
OL,7,Fbreach of the code of conduct by any
OL,8,Fmember of the Senedd to be a serious
OL,9,Fmatter".
OL,11,F"The reputation of the Senedd as an
OL,12,Finstitution, and the public's trust
OL,13,Fand confidence in it, rely upon
OL,14,Fmembers demonstrating integrity and
OL,15,Fleadership through their actions."
OL,17,FThe Welsh Conservatives have been
OL,18,Fapproached by ITV Wales for a comment.
